\id 3JN - Mufian NT (Balif dialect) -Papua New Guinea 1988 (web version -2013 bd)
\h 3 Jon
\toc1 Basef Ifimba Jon Nagiꞌ Nandaꞌafi Fagafeꞌma Wanifi
\toc2 3 Jon
\toc3 3 Jo
\mt1 Basef Ifimba Jon Nagiꞌ Nandaꞌafi Fagafeꞌma Wanifi
\iot Basef bandafi fagafeꞌma wanifi Jon nandaꞌafi
\io1 ves 1-4 Jon nasapaꞌ dagala ananini naloma basef buꞌwafi ma nogatopalopa alipunai Gaius
\io1 ves 5-8 Jon nanifela Gaiusa nandaꞌ waf buꞌwafi
\io1 ves 9-10 Diotrefes nandaꞌ waf awafi
\io1 ves 11-12 Demitrius nandaꞌ waf buꞌwafi
\io1 ves 13-15 Basef duꞌwanif akutaifi
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Aeꞌ agiliwai igimafi esis Kristeni andaꞌ anif basef fafeꞌmago inaꞌ alipinai Gaius. Aeꞌ okom maimailina endilisi aꞌowaꞌ.\x * \xo 1:1 \xt 2 Jo 1\x*
\v 2 Inaꞌ alipinai, andabetena Goda hiahawes hiasi inaꞌ nandaꞌasi sogataga boꞌwes andeandeꞌma aowas akana negape andeandeꞌ siꞌi ambal ineꞌili lagape andeandeꞌ.\x * \xo 1:2 \xt 2 Jo 4\x*
\v 3 Fowaꞌ aeꞌ ameꞌ basefa anom alipumi mafiꞌi matagame maꞌipi waf ineꞌifi maꞌi inaꞌ naila basef endilisifi datima. Ameꞌ basef ifimba andagalamena aꞌowaꞌ.
\v 4 Aeꞌ sonahe aꞌowaꞌ ma awasi sagaila basef endilisifi. Apaꞌ aeꞌ ina sonahe ma anis hiahawes daias sikilaꞌ sonagahema isimba, owaꞌatin.
\s1 Gaius nandaꞌ maol buꞌwani Godi
\p 
\v 5 Alipinai aeꞌ okom magamagailinai, maol hiani inaꞌ nandaꞌani ma nagatopalopa amom sahin owani, inimba inaꞌ nandaꞌan datima endilisi. Amom ina nati nogohnaepima negawam, owaꞌ. Apaꞌ inaꞌ natolom numafiam atin.\x * \xo 1:5 \xt Ta 3:13\x*
\v 6 Amom hiami maꞌipa esis Kristen sagape naꞌai ma okom ineꞌimi maimailam negatopalopam. Aeꞌ ahaliꞌina ma negatopalopama gwaꞌaisi otamba mais mofaꞌas atin mogafeꞌ anagon mondaꞌ maol Godi siꞌi okom ananimi magaꞌi.\x * \xo 1:6 \xt 1 Ko 9:12,15\x*
\v 7 Deiꞌ main, amom mafeꞌ mandaꞌ maola agol Kraisi, apaꞌ ina mofaꞌ gwaꞌaisi maisa esis isimba sogololama Godi, owaꞌ.
\v 8 Isimba atis apaꞌ aꞌ mondatopalopama gwaꞌaisi maisa mondaꞌ maola basef endilisifi Kraisi mogalomam.
\s1 Anona aman Diotrefes nandaꞌ waf awafi
\p 
\v 9 Aeꞌ andaꞌ anif basef fafeꞌmago esis Kristen, apaꞌ Diotrefes anen aꞌ okom maꞌimaꞌi aꞌowaꞌ ma nogape dembinai nigaliꞌi. Anen ina naila basef aeꞌafi, owaꞌatin.
\v 10 Nemaf mamahefa aeꞌ iꞌi egafeꞌmago inaꞌ, aeꞌ ewalapa basefa waf hiafi afamba anen nandaꞌafi. Anen nambasoꞌmas naꞌi basef fafifafi awafi findiwaefa aeꞌ. Apaꞌ ina nandaꞌ waf afamba atef, owaꞌatin. Nandaꞌ anef wapani naꞌamba. Nowaꞌ alafugama amom sahin owan magawalipasa basef Godi maꞌi mogafiꞌmai anini. Eaꞌ anef wapani naꞌamba. Nasopama anis Kristen daias saꞌi sogatopalopa amom amambai nelefatas safeꞌ sape andoꞌ ma sios.\x * \xo 1:10 \xt 1 Jo 3:6-10\x*
\s1 Demitrius nandaꞌ waf buꞌwafi
\p 
\v 11 Inaꞌ alipinai, owaꞌi nila waf awafia, hapaifi. Nindaila buꞌwafi atef. Epen ami nandaꞌ waf buꞌwafi, anin epen Godi. Apaꞌ ami nandaꞌ waf awafii, anin ina negawa God, owaꞌatin.\x * \xo 1:11 \xt Jo 19:35\x*
\p 
\v 12 Epes hiasi sagasaꞌma agol Demitriusi. Waf ananifi endilisifi fihimbaꞌmapa anen aman buꞌunai. Aeꞌ wapani aꞌi anen buꞌunai eaꞌ inaꞌ negawa basef aeꞌafi endilisifi.\x * \xo 1:12 \xt 2 Jo 12\x*
\s1 Basef ifimba duꞌwanif akutaifi
\p 
\v 13 Aeꞌ aꞌi iꞌipina basef hiafi hiꞌilif, apaꞌ aeꞌ andaiwaꞌma endaꞌ pen endaꞌef fil pepa fegafeꞌmago inaꞌ, owaꞌ.
\v 14 Aeꞌ okom maꞌi atiasi efoꞌo itilina, dao afaꞌ biafa ondatima wiꞌi basef ifimba.
\p 
\v 15 Aeꞌ aꞌi opaf ineꞌifi fope awanef nepe andeandeꞌ. Alipisi ineꞌisi sagape naꞌaꞌe sandaꞌmenago dagala sandagalamago inaꞌ. Inaꞌ daꞌmasago dagala aeꞌani wapani nefeꞌmago esis sagape wambel ineꞌimbili atona atin. Eaꞌ maꞌuf. 
